Class SectorLines

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.badlogic.gdx.scenes.scene2d.Actor
      • se300.destinytactics.ui.SectorLines

  • public class SectorLines
extends com.badlogic.gdx.scenes.scene2d.Actor
    Author:
    Chris Shannon Extends Actor in the LibGDX framework. Draws lines connecting the sector label and sector sprite. Lines are redrawn with changes in parallax actor location.
